'''''Clockwork Planet''''' (Japanese:'''クロックワーク・プラネット''') is a light novel written by Yuu Kamiya and Tsubaki Himana, and has derivative works.

==Original Work Info==
The light novel is written by Yuu Kamiya and Tsubaki Himana and illustrated by Shino. Kodansha has published four volumes of the novels since April 2013. 

===Plot===
Naoto's a high school dropout and brilliant amateur tinkerer. He lives in a world that has been so over-exploited that the entire surface has become one vast machine. When a box crashes into his home containing a female automaton, it's a harbinger of change that will rock the entire globe, and give Naoto his chance to be a hero.<ref>https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=18959</ref>

