==Derivative Works==
===Comic===
The comic is drawn by Kuro, and it has been serialized in Kodansha's ''Monthly Shōnen Sirius'' since 2013. 
===Anime===
The anime is made by XEBEC. 
====STAFF====
*Original Creator: Yuu Kamiya, Tsubaki Himana
*Original Character Design: Shino
*Director: Tsuyoshi Nagasawa
*Series Composition: Kenji Sugihara
*Character Design: Shuichi Shimamura
*Prop Design: Yoshitomo Hara
*Item Design: 原由知
*Worldview Setting: Yasumitsu Suetake, Kio Edamatsu
*Art design: Masahiro Kubota
*Art Director: Masatoshi Kai
*Color Key: Taeko Mizuno
*3DCG: Yuki Funakoshi
*Director of Photography: Kenji Takehara
*Editing: Masahiro Matsumura
*Sound Director: Satoshi Motoyama
*Music: Shu Kanematsu, Hanae Nakamura, Kaori Nakano, Satoshi Hōno
*Anime making: XEBEC

